Celebrate #NationalRumDay with the only rum that matters! The Bumbu Party Punch uses easy-to-get ingredients you may already have in your fridge!
 
1.5oz Bumbu
1.5oz pineapple juice
0.75oz orange juice
Club soda to fill
Mint and pineapple to garnish
 
**combine rum, pineapple, and orange into a shaker with ice. Shake then strain into a glass with ice. Top with club soda and garnish with a mint spring. Enjoy!
